{"tid":352611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做人係咪應該甘心就算","createTime":"2017-08-09T01:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T08:12:17.000Z","uid":26701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1be8c24464efa467e4ffae07583a4d2667bb41","tid":352611,"uid":26701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:43:08.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得自己唔開心來自唔甘心，<br />\n20幾歲小康之家有份工，萬幾蚊，<br />\n唔諗上車唔諗升職加人工，唔諗拍拖，<br />\n自己一個洗都過到活，但問題就係來自我地有慾望，有諗法想更加好，所以我地追求四萬蚊一個月，追求永遠唔會鐘意自己既人，所以我地唔快樂呢？<br />\n如果我唔追求自己目標，得過且過，我係咪會開心d?"},{"pid":"0a714202f638ea2caebd25c85eca2323959a1623","tid":352611,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:44:17.000Z","msg":"知足常樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但香港萬零蚊係連尊嚴都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1027f51cf2fa7b0ebadab8b7da61064d5d9e4cff","tid":352611,"uid":26701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>知足常樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但香港萬零蚊係連尊嚴都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你岩，唔好話女仔，同新認識既朋友講野聲都細d"},{"pid":"2d364dbe6ce4af9f7f3a800f248e9d5f09e79645","tid":352611,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"每個人對人生目標既追求都唔同既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c71959eb69e9a2964b1138fd4f888167bb12d40","tid":352611,"uid":26701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:53:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個人對人生目標既追求都唔同既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我唔配有我依家既目標囉，死慳死抵買下股票又唔郁，太高估自己，所以失望"},{"pid":"ab62f8bb7581fd9916cd60296a2112bc0101c128","tid":352611,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"一支公就唔好將目標set喺物質同安穩上"},{"pid":"aaf3a60ff577f30f800e8da56fef531a4671dffb","tid":352611,"uid":26701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一支公就唔好將目標set喺物質同安穩上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我好累，有期望會失望"},{"pid":"a16bb5dd1455df169b6714ca7ed1a874da75a624","tid":352611,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T08:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一支公就唔好將目標set喺物質同安穩上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打，我好累，有期望會失望</blockquote><br />\n記得有年行富士山<br />\n見到一對夫婦 因為老婆頭痛得太犀利<br />\n決定唔登頂落山<br />\n我同開同老公吹水 話&quot;上唔到頂 真係好可惜&quot;<br />\n跟住佢答咗我一句<br />\n&quot;唔緊要 由山腳到山頂 都係富士山&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果做到目的就係手段 我諗巴打就唔會噉諗"}]}